OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FSome late
OL,6,Fsunshine for most then a dry night
OL,7,Fwith occasional clear spells. Shallow
OL,8,Fmist and fog patches possible in low
OL,9,Flying areas around dawn with winds
OL,10,Flight.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FA dry day with some good
OL,13,Fsunny spells in the morning before
OL,14,Fcloud builds up for a time. Very warm.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FA dry
OL,17,Fand very warm few days with some sunny
OL,18,Fspells, and perhaps very hot on
OL,19,FThursday. Perhaps some thundery
OL,20,Fshowers later on Thursday and on Friday
